	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator 161. See MRR 2.493. Read T. Manlius Fab. or Fal. The name as written on the stone (SIG(3) 679, II) is # :.., perhaps the same as the # of II Maccab. 11.34. Probably patrician. (LRT)" .
